|GSpot = 9.0 of 10<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/rpg/finalfantasy12/review.html |title=Final Fantasy XII|author=GameSpot staff | date=2006-10-31| work= GameSpot | accessdate=2007-12-07}}</ref>
